subject: Important Update: Price Update Effective November 1st, 2024
body:
Dear Kyrian Steven



We hope this message finds you well. At Sendforce Logistics, we remain committed to providing you with the best possible service. In light of the recent increase in fuel prices and increase in operations cost, we have had to review our rates to ensure that we continue to serve you effectively and maintain the high standard of service you expect from us.

Effective from November 1st, 2024, there will be a slight adjustment in our service rates. This decision was not made lightly, but it is necessary to ensure that we can continue delivering the reliable and quality service you deserve. While we understand that price adjustments are never easy, this decision is necessary to ensure we can continue meeting your expectations and delivering the service you deserve.

We deeply appreciate your understanding and continued partnership during this time.  If you have any questions or concerns regarding the upcoming rate increase, please do not hesitate to contact our customer support team via info@sendforceng.com or 08089229932

Thank you for your trust and support.



The Sendforce Team.

subject: Don’t Let This Opportunity Slip Away…
body:

Can I be real with you for a minute?

Every day you wait is a day further from your dream of studying in the USA on a full scholarship. It’s easy to say, “I’ll do it later,” but time is moving fast. Scholarship deadlines are coming up, and the opportunities that exist today might not be there tomorrow.

Now imagine six months from now. Have you gotten your USA scholarship offers? Or are you still wishing you’d be in the USA one day?

I don’t want that for you, and I’m pretty sure you don’t either.

That’s why I created the Scholarship Accelerator. It’s designed to take the guesswork out of this process and give you a clear path to securing your scholarship (and visa). No more stress. No more confusion.

If you start now, you could be on track to changing your life in just a few weeks. The difference between those who succeed and those who don’t is simple—they take action. They decide their dreams are worth the effort.

And to help you take that first step, I’m offering a 20% discount on the Scholarship Accelerator, but only for the next 72 hours. This is your chance to get moving toward your goals—before it’s too late.

I don’t want you to miss out. Time is ticking, and opportunities like this don’t wait.

Use the Coupon code “FUNDED20” here to enjoy your discount. Let’s make your dream a reality.

You’ve got this!
